# Overlord skills data
#  Version 1.0 06.04.2010
# -------- Generic configuration parameters ---
# ITEM - (string): tag of a new skill
# NAME - (string): name for reports
# DESCRIPTION - (string): text for knowledge report
#
# COMBAT_SKILL -  combat skill flag
# MAGIC_SKILL -  magic skill flag
# BASIC_SKILL - basic skill flag
# LEVEL - (int): - number of experience points (study days * 100) needed to reach this level
									all parameters after "LEVEL" will relate to all levels after that
									but later they may be overwrititten on the next levels
# REQUIRES- (skill tag) (int):  skill and it's level required to start learning.
# CAPACITY - [movement mode tag] (int): capacity added by possesing skill
# STUDY_COST- (int):  price of one day studying
# LEARNING_PARADIGM - defines rules for learning skill
# USING_PARADIGM - degines
# TARGET

# WEIGHT - (int): weight
# PRICE - (int): formal price
# CAPACITY - [movement mode tag] (int): capacity added by possesing item
# EQUIP_CAPACITY [movement mode tag] (int): capacity added by equipping item
# EQUIP_CATEGORY (int) or (equipment slot tag): equipment slot
# EQUIP_CONDITION (condition keyword) ... : defines condition for equipment
# 								SKILL_CONDITION (skill tag) (int): skill and level

# USE_SKILL - (skill tag) (int): defines skill and it's level for learning scrolls
# COMBAT_ACTION - ( combat action tag): defines use in combat
# SPECIAL -  special item flag
# UNIQUE -  unique item flag
# LIVE -  live item flag
# MAGIC -  magic item flag
# -------- Stats ---
# MELEE - (int) : attack rating modificator
# INITIATIVE - (int): initiative modificator (more - better)
# DEFENSE - (int): defence rating modificator
# DAMAGE - (int): modificator
# DAMAGE_TYPE (int): or {AIR; EARTH; FIRE; VOID; WATER;} defines damage type
# MISSILE - (int): ranged attack rating modificator
# HITS - (int): number of hits modificator
# LIFE - (int): hit points modificator - NB: Do not use for combat actions - use effects
# MANA - (int): maximum mana modificator
# UPKEEP - (int): upkeep modificator
# CONTROL - (int): control points modificator
# STEALTH - (int): stealth modificator
# OBSERVATION - (int): observation modificator


# -------- Bonuses ---
# STUDY_BONUS (skill tag) (int): skill and bonus in % to speed of learning
# LEARNING_LEVEL_BONUS (skill tag) (int): skill and bonus to maximum level
# USE_BONUS (skill tag) (int): skill and bonus in % to effect of using
# MOVE_BONUS (movement mode tag) (int): movement bonus in % and mode it applies

# --------- Skill Use Types -----------
# USING_CRAFT
# USING_HARVEST
# USING_CONSTRUCTION
# USING_BUILD
# USING_ENCHANT
# USING_SUMMON

# ---COMBAT_ACTION
# MELEE
# RANGED
COMBAT_SUMMON
COMBAT_ENCHANT

# --------- Skill Learning  Types -----------
# LEARNING_NORMAL
# LEARNING_MAGIC can be learned only by leaders <not implemented>
# LEARNING_ELEMENTAL_MAGIC can be learned only if sertain magecraft level is gained
# LEARNING_CREATURE - only creatures can learn

# --------- Special cases  -----------

# USE_ANYONE - Anyone can use this skill. No need to study.
# NO_EXP - Using of this skill grants no experience
# NO_LEARN - Skill can't be learned

